🛒 Core Shop Features
 Product grid (all clothes displayed properly)
 Product cards (image, name, price, button)
 Add to cart button for each product
 Cart sidebar / cart page
 Cart quantity system (+ / - items)
 Remove item from cart
 Total price calculation


🔍 Search & Filtering
 Search bar (filter products by name)
 Category filters (e.g. hoodies, pants, shoes)
 Price sorting (low → high / high → low)
 Reset filters button


🎨 UI / Design System
 Improved product card design
 Hover animations on products/buttons
 Responsive layout (mobile + desktop)
 Clean spacing + typography system


🧠 App Logic Improvements
 Products stored in an array (data-driven UI)
 Render function (UI generated from data)
 Event delegation (one click handler system)
 Dataset usage for product IDs
 LocalStorage for cart saving 

🔐 Login System (fake frontend auth)
 Login page UI
 "Fake login" (store user in localStorage)
 Show username when logged in
 Logout button


💳 Checkout (simple version)
 Checkout button in cart
 Checkout summary page/modal
 Clear cart after checkout
 Order confirmation message


🚀 Optional “Flex” Features (if you finish early)
 Wishlist (save items)
 Recently viewed products
 Product animations (fade-in / slide)
 Dark mode toggle
 Loading animation when rendering products
 
🧠 How to use this

Don’t try to build randomly. Go in this order:

Products + render system
Cart logic
Search/filter
UI polish
Login
Checkout
Extras